@startuml 联合应用时序图

actor 用户
participant "Main" as main
participant "ShelfTemplateFactory" as factory
participant "ConcreteShelfTemplate" as template
participant "Shelf" as shelf
participant "NormalPicking" as normalPick
participant "WavePickingDecorator" as wavePick
participant "ColdChainPickingDecorator" as coldPick
participant "NormalPutaway" as normalPut
participant "BatchControlDecorator" as batchPut
participant "ExpiryPriorityDecorator" as expiryPut

用户 -> main: 启动程序

== 1. 获取货架模板（享元模式） ==
main -> factory: getTemplate("驶入式")
factory --> main: template1(首次创建)
main -> factory: getTemplate("驶入式")
factory --> main: template1(复用)

main -> shelf: new Shelf("S-W-001", "D区", template1)
main -> shelf: display()
shelf -> template: display("S-W-001", "D区")
template --> shelf: 货架编号:S-W-001, 库区:D区 | 模板类型:驶入式...
shelf --> main: 完整货架信息

== 2. 执行拣货（装饰器模式） ==
main -> normalPick: new NormalPicking()
main -> wavePick: new WavePickingDecorator(normalPick)
main -> coldPick: new ColdChainPickingDecorator(wavePick)

main -> coldPick: execute()
coldPick -> wavePick: execute()
wavePick -> normalPick: execute()
normalPick --> wavePick: "按库位顺序拣货"
wavePick --> coldPick: "按库位顺序拣货 -> 按波次聚合订单批量拣货"
coldPick --> main: "按库位顺序拣货 -> 按波次聚合订单批量拣货 -> 低温管控、限定拣货月台"

== 3. 执行上架（装饰器模式） ==
main -> normalPut: new NormalPutaway()
main -> batchPut: new BatchControlDecorator(normalPut)
main -> expiryPut: new ExpiryPriorityDecorator(batchPut)

main -> expiryPut: execute()
expiryPut -> batchPut: execute()
batchPut -> normalPut: execute()
normalPut --> batchPut: "空闲库位就近上架"
batchPut --> expiryPut: "空闲库位就近上架 -> 同批次集中存放"
expiryPut --> main: "空闲库位就近上架 -> 同批次集中存放 -> 近效期放外侧"

== 4. 验证享元复用 ==
main -> factory: getCreationCount()
factory --> main: 4(仅4种模板各创建1个)

用户 <-- main: 打印完整结果
@enduml
